quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  18,94,"Wọ́n sọ pé: “Thul-Ƙọrneen, dájúdájú (ìran) Ya’jūj àti Ma’jūj ń ṣe ìbàjẹ́ lórí ilẹ̀. Ṣé kí á fún ọ ní owó-òde nítorí kí o lè bá wa mọ odi kan sáààrin àwa àti àwọn?”"
  18,95,"Ó sọ pé: “Ohun tí Olúwa mi fún mi nínú ipò lóore jùlọ. Nítorí náà, ẹ fi agbára ràn mí lọ́wọ́ ni nítorí kí n̄g lè mọ odi sáààrin ẹ̀yin àti àwọn."
  18,96,"Ẹ máa fún mi ni ègígé irin títí di ìgbà tí ó fi máa bá ẹ̀gbẹ́ àpáta méjèèjì dọ́gba.” Ó sọ pé: “Ẹ máa fẹ́ atẹ́gùn ẹwìrì (sí i lára) títí di ìgbà tí ó máa (pọ́n wẹ̀ẹ̀ bí) iná.” Ó sọ pé: “Ẹ mu idẹ wá fún mi kí n̄g yọ́ ọ lé e lórí.”"
  19,55,"Ó máa ń pa ará ilé rẹ̀ ní àṣẹ ìrun kíkí àti Zakāh yíyọ. Ó sì jẹ́ ẹni ìyọ́nú lọ́dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ̀."
  19,56,"Sọ ìtàn (Ànábì) ’Idrīs tí ó wà nínú al-Ƙur’ān. Dájúdájú ó jẹ́ olódodo pọ́nńbélé, (ó sì jẹ́) Ànábì."
  19,57,"A sì gbé e sí àyè gíga (nínú sánmọ̀)."
  20,37,"Àti pé dájúdájú A ti ṣe oore fún ọ nígbà kan rí."
  20,38,"(Rántí) nígbà tí A ṣípayá ohun tí A ṣípayá fún ìyá rẹ"
  20,39,"pé: “Ju Mūsā sínú àpótí. Kí o sì gbé e jù sínú odò. Odò yó sì gbé e jù sí etí odò. Ọ̀tá Mi àti ọ̀tá rẹ̀ sì máa gbé e.” Mo sì da ìfẹ́ láti ọ̀dọ̀ Mi bò ọ́ nítorí kí wọ́n lè tọ́jú rẹ lójú Mi.”"
  21,13,"Ẹ má ṣe sá lọ. Ẹ padà síbi n̄ǹkan tí A fi ṣe gbẹdẹmukẹ fún yín àti àwọn ibùgbé yín nítorí kí A lè bi yín ní ìbéèrè."
  21,14,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Ègbé wa ò! Dájúdájú àwa jẹ́ alábòsí.”"
  21,15,"Igbe wọn yìí kò dúró títí A fi sọ wọ́n di koríko tí wọ́n gé, wọ́n sì dòkú kalẹ̀."